日至今年一月七日到訪廣東省順德，並於當地一診所求醫。他於一月十日至十四日到訪澳門並即日往返。病人的太太、女兒及兒子沒有出現病徵，將被送往麥理浩夫人度假村接受隔離監測。衞生防護中心正跟進接觸者追蹤的工作。調查仍然進行中。"},{"pid":"1aa27be416d5cfce9e2bc3e149d92c8417abfccc","tid":1873404,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48915d3d8fa75fb41c1a7137a541175f18d8af87","tid":1873404,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:02:02.000Z","msg":"唔封關 而家開始爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"依家仲要只係爆緊一月尾，仲有二月頭返嚟香港個批"},{"pid":"ba691c0d6595939ae25f02fac8d521523b4a90d4","tid":1873404,"uid":63491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3147aa55f7329efb5b1e87b8a331bbda291b7ef","tid":1873404,"uid":53248,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"其實打邊爐個家人只係冰山一角<br />\n應該仲有好多冇乜病徵冇睇醫生<br />\n不停傳緊比人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"可能中左招，輕微徵狀，好番都無人知"},{"pid":"4cbe0638e5a381b50514a845e612f793df393417","tid":1873404,"uid":81325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ure79Xy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fure79Xy.png&h=c3942d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望冇事啦"},{"pid":"17ebfe9e541d945b40af1c6693f5cfe97441378c","tid":1873404,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43df5f19af0b1e431badec02ac63037fb5af3cfc","tid":1873404,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582b5dabf4f8134539316eba0754717e3b5affd2","tid":1873404,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd0c81cdc09626a99a9011f159a2f700c35262cc","tid":1873404,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"唔比一齊去旅行惹番來咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:11:41.000Z","m